Title: S20:E4 - How to transition from the arts into a career in tech (Jessica Wilkins)
Description: In this episode, we talk about how to transition from the arts into a career in tech, with Jessica Wilkins, software developer at This Dot Labs, technical writer at Free Code Camp, and former professional classical musician.
